Description: The world of genetic understanding is growing. Let's navigate it together.
Full Description: Advanced Tele-Genetic Counseling (AT-GC) is a national leader in genetic counseling and a pioneer in the field of genetic telemedicine. We are dedicated to the development of the tele-genetics healthcare market as a means by which we can help increase comprehensive genetic counseling access to all patients nationwide. At AT-GC, we know that each person’s unique story is recorded in the language of his or her DNA. It’s our job to help tell these stories, one genome at a time. Advanced Tele-Genetic Counseling offers comprehensive genetics consultations and unparalleled expertise in genetic testing implementation and interpretation, all through telemedicine. With our focus on thorough, compassionate, and ethical care, we strive to treat each patient with the utmost respect as they navigate the world of hereditary conditions and personalized genomics. We believe that all people should have equal access to genetic counseling services, and by utilizing telemedicine as the platform through which we connect with patients and providers, we are turning our passion into reality.  Our focus is on personalized prevention and education of the health effects of genetic findings. Learning one's genetic status often provides explanations for hereditary symptoms and encourages a focus on management and healthy living.  Unique to our industry, AT-GC is founded and actively managed by certified genetic counselors. As both businesspeople and clinical counselors, we are in an exceptional position to understand and excel in the rapidly expanding world of genetics and biotechnology. With unsurpassed expertise and professionalism, we are committed to providing compassionate and informed, personalized genetics services to our patients. Our operational model is highly flexible, allowing for seamless integration of services, tailored to accommodate the specific needs of your company. Individual referrals are also welcome. With specialized knowledge and skill base, our team of highly specialized and board-certified genetic counselors and medical professionals is well-versed in expertly navigating the charted and uncharted oceans of genetic information, providing genetic knowledge to all patients while expanding their whole body health knowledge, and empowering them to make fully informed health choices. We are equally committed to promoting positive relationships with our referring institutions and partner companies. At AT-GC, we realize that like our individual genomes, no two genetic companies or practices are exactly the same. To discuss collaboration and customized partnership options and bring genetic counseling care to your patient population, please contact us. Institutional, self-pay, and insurance billing options (in select locations) are available. This means that whether you are seeking a genetic counseling referral source without monetary commitment, or whether you would like to arrange personalized, ongoing genetic counseling support for your patient groups at a competitive institutional rate, we can accommodate the specific needs of your institution.  The world of genetic understanding is changing. Let's navigate it together.  From the team at Advanced Tele-Genetic Counseling, we look forward to connecting with you.

Full Description: Early in my life I was taught that if you could build a better mousetrap, the world would beat a path to your door. This is it. In an industry whose stock valuations are exploding as you read this.     We are developing a process called Ionic Migration Leaching to recover metals from subterranean deposits using in-situ electrodes to collect, precipitate, and remove metal ions. This revolutionary process can be powered by solar, wind or natural gas fuel cell produced electricity. Our technology is benign to the environment causing minimal disturbance as only the desired metals are extracted and removed leaving original rock strata in place and untouched. In essence this technique reverses the natural processes that formed the deposits in the first place.    A deposit containing in excess of $500 million value of uranium has been identified and is being acquired. This deposit is within an area identified by a US government agency as containing an estimated 200 million pounds of uranium resources. These resources were thought to be too low grade to produce in the past. Ionic Migration Leaching would make them profitable to extract at current prices.     This investment should be viewed as high risk - high reward. If we are successful, early investors could receive a return of ten to one or more. If we are not successful, they could lose all of their investment. We desire only investors who understand this concept.

Description: Law firm specializing in all aspects of business law (formation, raising money, business acquisitions).
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: We understand that businesses face a wide range of legal challenges on a daily basis. Whether you are starting a new business, expanding your operations, or facing a legal dispute, our team of attorneys has the expertise and knowledge to guide you through the process. Our practice areas include corporate law, contract law, private placements, employment law, and securities. We provide a broad range of services to our clients, including legal advice, contract drafting and negotiation, regulatory compliance, intellectual property protection, employment law counseling, and dispute resolution. Corporate Law:  We are experienced in helping businesses of all sizes with their legal needs, including formation, governance, and transactions. We advise clients on the choice of entity, formation of corporations, limited liability companies, and partnerships. We also provide counsel on corporate governance, compliance, and management. We have the expertise to advise clients on mergers and acquisitions, asset and stock purchases, and other transactions. Contract Law: Contracts are the foundation of every business relationship. We work with clients to draft, review, and negotiate contracts that protect their interests and help them achieve their business objectives. We assist clients with a wide range of contracts, including supply agreements, distribution agreements, licensing agreements, and employment contracts. Employment Law: Employment law is a critical aspect of every business's operations. We work with clients to ensure compliance with federal and state laws governing employment, including wage and hour regulations, discrimination, and harassment laws. We advise clients on hiring and firing, employment contracts, and employee benefits. We pride ourselves on providing personalized attention to each of our clients. We take the time to understand their business objectives, and we work tirelessly to achieve their goals. Our attorneys are committed to providing high-quality legal services, and we strive to be a trusted advisor to our clients. If you are in need of legal assistance with any aspect of business law, we invite you to contact us to schedule a consultation. We look forward to working with you.
